# github.com/docker/docker v28.5.2+incompatible is a test-only INDIRECT dep,
# pulled via github.com/golang-migrate/migrate/v4/database/postgres (test) →
# github.com/dhui/dktest, which spins up a PostgreSQL container for migration
# integration tests. The Docker client is never imported by production code and
# requires local daemon access not present in the deployed image.
